                                            },
                                            "Articles": {
                                                "val": "0"
                                            },
                                            "Text": {
                                                "val": "Support the execution of Test and Evaluation DT and OT schedule per the TEMP.  Continue execution of DT Phase DT-B.  Develop Test Plans for OT Phase OT-C, Initial Operational Test and Evaluation (IOT&E).  Conduct Detailed Design Survivability Assessment in support of shot selection for Damage Scenario Based Engineering Analysis (DSBEA) and Final Vulnerability Assessment Report (FSAR).  Coordinate efforts with NAVSEA, MSC, PEO Ships, COMOPTEVFOR, JITC and OSD DOT&E."
                                            }
